2.0.0.name: wordpress/webtrends
2.0.0.description:
Webtrends founded the web analytics industry in 1993. Today, their leadership extends to measurement, optimization and integration of all digital content, including web sites, social media and paid-search advertising.

This Webtrends WordPress plugin allows Webtrends customers to: * Automatically add the necessary JavaScript to their WordPress footer for tracking * With an API Key entered, allows users to view their Analytics data in a WordPress dashboard.
